data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of tranquility! This traditional two-story abode boasts four spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths, providing ample space for your family to thrive. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm ambiance of the family room, offering views of the kitchen and a cozy fireplace, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring stained cabinets, plenty of counter space, and an inviting eat-in area, ideal for casual meals or morning coffee. Entertain guests in style with the formal living room and dining room, where cherished memories are waiting to be made. Retreat to the luxurious master suite upstairs, complete with a tray ceiling and a private bath, offering a serene oasis after a long day. Additional spacious bedrooms provide comfort and privacy for the entire family. Step outside to discover your own private paradise—a patio overlooking a huge backyard with direct access to the tranquil pond. Whether you're hosting summer barbecues or enjoying peaceful evenings by the water, this outdoor space offers endless possibilities for relaxation and recreation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this retreat your forever home! Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning the endless possibilities that await you in this serene haven. $5000 towards closing cost incentive.
